scenes.description: Mori Calliope stands in a dark environment with floating debris, announcing her intention to visit a resort and inviting her fans, the 'Dead Beats,' to join her.
Calliope approaches the entrance of a grand resort, showing off her ability to walk on water and displaying the logo on the back of her jacket.
Calliope enters the resort's pool area, activates a panoramic camera view, finds a bar, and poses for screenshots while reminding viewers to use her 5th-anniversary hashtag.
